Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,00:00:10.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Class 3-B, Kurumi Ebisuzawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,00:00:12.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,00:00:24.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,00:00:28.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't slack off! It's not gonna clean itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,00:00:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But the floor's so slippery, Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,00:00:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ya moron, call me Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,00:00:39.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whaa...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,00:00:42.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're getting way too into this today, Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,00:00:44.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Call me Sarge, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,00:00:48.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll show you how it's done! \NFollow me, Private Takeya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,00:00:50.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,00:00:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,00:00:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,00:00:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,00:01:02.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to slip and fall, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,00:01:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it- whaaaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,00:01:06.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop, stop! \NGot it- whaaaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,00:01:11.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,00:01:12.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,00:01:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow, where the hell were you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,00:01:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's just so slimy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,00:01:21.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,00:01:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those two sure are energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,00:01:29.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing Yuki-chan had an extra swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,00:01:31.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,00:01:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not happy to be dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,00:01:38.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Why did you even bring these back \Nfrom the mall in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,00:01:40.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could've brought something you needed instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,00:01:42.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,00:01:45.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we are girls, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,00:01:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,CONFIDENTIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Faculty Emergency Evacuation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Only open this manual when:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption5,,0,0,0,,-  The principal or other official has ordered it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption6,,0,0,0,,-  An A-1 warning has been issued
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,00:01:51.25,Caption7,,0,0,0,,-  No outside communication has been received for more than 10 days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,00:01:52.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We just found out about that yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,00:01:56.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it alright to be goofing off despite that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,00:01:59.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow! Taromaru's butt is wiping it clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,00:02:00.33,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern, \Nbut let's avoid thinking about it for now. \NWow! Taromaru's butt is wiping it clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,00:02:02.95,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern, \Nbut let's avoid thinking about it for now. \NAlright, you're promoted to Second Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,00:02:03.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern, \Nbut let's avoid thinking about it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,00:02:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's such good weather for a swim, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,00:02:12.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Umm, this isn't a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,00:02:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the water storage tank, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,00:02:21.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,00:02:24.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,00:02:26.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,When you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,00:02:27.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Let's do it together! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,00:02:30.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,00:02:33.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,00:02:37.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,00:02:37.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,00:02:40.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,00:02:57.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,You know what you have to do after school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,00:02:58.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,00:03:00.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak off to go home! (Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,00:03:03.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,How about club? Let's get something done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,00:03:05.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Don't go playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,00:03:09.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,That girl says "I'm back" (Welcome back!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,00:03:13.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine as long as we're together (Club!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,00:03:16.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Everybody say: let's all be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,00:03:17.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Cause you wanna do it, if you wanna do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,00:03:19.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,when you wanna do it, you wanna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,00:03:21.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,I love you so much! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,00:03:24.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are enjoying our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,00:03:27.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,We're having fun 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,00:03:30.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,The red sun shines bright on the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,00:03:34.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried shouting out to it (We're doing great!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,00:03:37.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,We are right here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,00:03:40.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,We have dreams here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,00:03:43.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,00:03:43.70,Caption2,,0,0,0,,you're talking about your friends! (That's right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,00:03:46.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,I tried saying "I love you!" (I love you so much!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,00:03:53.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Vacation Day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,00:03:55.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,That morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,00:03:59.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,CONFIDENTIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,00:03:59.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Faculty Emergency Evacuation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,00:03:59.04,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,00:03:59.04,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Only open this manual when:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,00:03:59.04,Caption5,,0,0,0,,-  The principal or other official has ordered it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,00:03:59.04,Caption6,,0,0,0,,-  An A-1 warning has been issued
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,00:03:59.04,Caption7,,0,0,0,,-  No outside communication has been received for more than 10 days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,00:04:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you get any sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,00:04:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to sleep after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,00:04:06.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,00:04:12.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, that key had Megu-nee's name on it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,00:04:13.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,00:04:17.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So that means Megu-nee knew about \Neverything from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,00:04:21.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She knew what was happening and hid it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,00:04:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,00:04:26.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,00:04:27.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,00:04:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think that probably wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,00:04:35.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The front says not to open it \Nexcept in certain times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,00:04:40.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They might've been given it a long time ago, \Nso even if she read it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,00:04:44.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,...It might not make a difference \Nafter it all happened, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,00:04:47.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,God dammit! Is it a virus or \Na biological weapon or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,00:04:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going crazy just trying to figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,00:04:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of interesting things written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,00:04:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Emergency evacuation areas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,00:05:01.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are two more floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,00:05:06.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you didn't know that, that means \Nyou haven't gone down there yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,00:05:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,00:05:11.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,00:05:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, let's do some cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,00:05:20.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,O-oh, Yuki-chan, I thought you were \Ntaking Taromaru on a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,00:05:23.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's this about cleaning all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,00:05:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,00:05:30.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I let Taromaru off his leash on the roof, \Nand he jumped right into the pond!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,00:05:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Again? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,00:05:34.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,00:05:36.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Let's all graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,00:05:36.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Everyone write 100 pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,00:05:36.04,Caption3,,0,0,0,,I can't write that many!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,00:05:38.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, Senpai, can you be a little more careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,00:05:39.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,00:05:44.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's soooo dirty in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,00:05:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are fish living in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,00:05:48.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel so bad for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,00:05:51.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, it's warm out today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,00:05:54.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,so why don't we get wet and \Nclean out the water tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,00:05:56.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna end up playing in it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,00:05:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh! That would be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,00:06:01.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,00:06:04.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you got Taromaru dirty on purpose \Nso you could go play in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,00:06:09.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,O-of course not! Taromaru just looked like \Nhe was enjoying the water so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,00:06:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You felt like playing in the water too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,00:06:14.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just a little! Just a tiny little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,00:06:18.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai, we don't have time to be-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,00:06:20.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,00:06:21.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,00:06:26.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's go clean out the water storage tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,00:06:27.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really, Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,00:06:31.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup. We did just buy those bathing suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,00:06:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,00:06:35.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Taromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,00:06:38.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You should get clean first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,00:06:40.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,00:06:41.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,00:06:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think we need some time to get our thoughts sorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,00:06:49.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot to think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,00:06:51.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,between Megu-nee and our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,00:06:59.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan, that's weird, you're the kind of girl \Nwho looks thinner with clothes on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,00:07:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't say that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,00:07:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y..Yuri-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,00:07:06.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,00:07:08.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,N-no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,00:07:14.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow! The sky's so blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,00:07:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, what great weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,00:07:18.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,00:07:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ewww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,00:07:27.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Nobody's been taking care of it, \Nso algae just grew and grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,00:07:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's a lot of sand and silt in it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,00:07:33.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,00:07:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, this is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,00:07:38.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this pond here for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,00:07:39.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's called a biotope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,00:07:45.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,A freshwater ecosystem was placed \Nin this water collection tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,00:07:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They often use it in biology classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,00:07:49.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,00:07:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of fish are in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,00:07:55.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rainbow trout and carp, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,00:07:59.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get the fish into the buckets \Nand start cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,00:08:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,00:08:21.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,00:08:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pool's open for business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,00:08:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,00:08:34.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's not like a real pool. \NThe bottom is bare concrete, so you shouldn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,00:08:37.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,00:08:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,00:08:43.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, no fair, Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,00:08:45.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you shouldn't jump-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,00:08:51.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm drow... I'm drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,00:08:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,00:08:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right! My feet touch the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,00:09:05.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's weird, it doesn't smell like the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,00:09:09.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You moron, the pool smells like the chlorine \Nthey put in to keep it clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,00:09:10.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,00:09:14.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Will the fish be okay with chlorine in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,00:09:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,People don't put fish in pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,00:09:21.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it'd kinda be cool if there were fish in pools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,00:09:23.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want to swim with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,00:09:26.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd swim with them, and if I got hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,00:09:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'd eat them alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,00:09:29.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,Grumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,00:09:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,00:09:32.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got you now! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,00:09:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,00:09:38.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm taking another look at it, \Nit's pretty big, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,00:09:40.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at his belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,00:09:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ri-san, what're those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,00:10:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are solar panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,00:10:02.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're solar panels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,00:10:04.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They make electricity from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,00:10:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They let us have a normal life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,00:10:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,00:10:13.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have a water purifier too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,00:10:17.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,There are machines that filter \Nriver water and ground water, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,00:10:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,00:10:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Gardening Club took place on the roof, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,00:10:25.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megurigaoka High is its own town,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,00:10:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and the students are its citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,00:10:33.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,These citizens can carry out various jobs \Nthat help make the town self-sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,00:10:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You read that in the school information book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,00:10:39.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I read it so many times I ended up memorizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,00:10:42.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though there are only four of us citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,00:10:48.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many people they imagined \Nthis school supporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,00:10:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everything just seems so perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,00:10:54.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,00:10:59.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Almost like they expected this \Nto happen from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,00:11:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the conversation here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,00:11:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We said we were gonna have fun today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,00:11:07.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,00:11:09.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,00:11:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,00:11:13.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru, you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,00:11:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,00:11:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ooh, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,00:11:25.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Miki, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,00:11:25.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,00:11:27.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,00:11:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nice volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,00:11:29.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's a toss-up! This is a volley! \NNice volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,00:11:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a toss-up! This is a volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,00:11:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright then, watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,00:11:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,00:11:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't hit it too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,00:11:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go for the spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,00:11:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then just toss it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,00:11:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't need to fake us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,00:11:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,00:11:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,00:11:44.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,00:11:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's way off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,00:11:47.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,00:11:51.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Kohai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,00:11:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta take it seriously, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,00:11:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,00:11:58.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,00:11:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,00:12:01.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,00:12:02.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,00:12:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,00:12:06.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got, it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,00:12:08.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,00:12:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,00:12:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Yuki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,00:12:29.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,00:12:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,00:12:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,00:12:39.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it? Is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,00:12:41.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,00:12:45.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that I think about it, we did have those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,00:12:48.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Water guns, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,00:12:51.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're those doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,00:12:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Someone brought them here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,00:12:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,00:13:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you tell me one last thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,00:13:06.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,00:13:10.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're a pretty skilled gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,00:13:12.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've got a nickname, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,00:13:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do I, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,00:13:23.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why's it gotten all serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,00:13:30.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And here you were, going on about \Nhow it was someone else's toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,00:13:36.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I bet they're yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,00:13:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,00:13:41.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on two things you ought to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,00:13:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Number 1: You did an excellent job firing rapidly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,00:13:50.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but exactly how many shots are \Nleft in those guns, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,00:13:55.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Number 2: I do have a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,00:13:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They call me the Water Balloon Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,00:14:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,00:14:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,00:14:04.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,00:14:10.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! She bounced the water balloons away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,00:14:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,00:14:14.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And now, our final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,00:14:16.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,00:14:27.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,00:14:28.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,00:14:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,00:14:40.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai, you're getting too carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,00:14:42.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,00:14:44.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just got so into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,00:14:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were so cool, Ri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,00:14:48.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna be a witch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,00:14:51.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do you become a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,00:14:54.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Let's see, first you have to \Ncontract with a demon, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,00:15:01.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, go fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,00:15:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,00:15:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,00:15:06.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,00:15:12.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,00:15:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, it's your CD player, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,00:15:18.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,00:15:22.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I took it because I wanted to \Ntry out the radio function.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,00:15:25.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's alright. Did you pick up anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,00:15:30.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd get better reception on the roof, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,00:15:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,00:15:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,00:15:50.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not picking up any stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,00:15:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,00:15:54.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,00:15:59.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You'll hurt your ears if you keep \Nblasting that noise on your headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,00:16:03.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about me. \NJust use the speakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,00:16:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,00:16:06.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,00:16:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,00:16:18.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,00:16:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you smell Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,00:17:01.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think he wants you to play with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,00:17:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,00:17:21.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,00:17:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The wind's getting cold, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,00:17:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,00:17:35.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, you two, shall we wrap it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,00:17:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,00:17:50.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's pretty clean now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,00:17:53.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now Taromaru can jump in \Nand it won't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,00:17:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please don't let him jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,00:18:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,00:18:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sound just like an old man, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,00:18:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,00:18:20.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,00:18:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's school, so we've only got showers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,00:18:28.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I think the sports clubs had a bath \Nthey could use in the club building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,00:18:32.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It'd be a bit of a hassle getting \Nall the way out there just for a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,00:18:37.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,00:18:40.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,00:18:43.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,00:18:45.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,00:18:47.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,00:18:49.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not that, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,00:18:53.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you're worried about something, \Nyou can just ask us to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,00:18:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're your senpai, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,00:18:58.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I don't know how comfortable I'd feel \Nrelying on your help, Yuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,00:19:03.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'd be a big help! So let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,00:19:06.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, that hurts. You're so rude, Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,00:19:09.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You need to cake responsibility \Nand respect your senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,00:19:12.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean "take"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,00:19:12.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Take
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,00:19:12.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,00:19:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine then. You be the senpai then, Mii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,00:19:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,00:19:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh jeez, don't sulk, Yuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,00:19:24.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You won't say mean things anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,00:19:25.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,00:19:27.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll ask me for advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,00:19:28.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,00:19:32.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's this friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,00:19:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,00:19:39.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,She was my classmate. We got along real well. \NShe was really energetic and positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,00:19:43.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And we were always together, \Nbut lately I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,00:19:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's not coming to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,00:19:47.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,00:19:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you should have more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,00:19:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,00:19:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you hate school, Mii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,00:19:56.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,00:19:59.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right? I love school, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,00:20:03.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're here, and Ri-san's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,00:20:06.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and Kurumi-chan's here, and Megu-nee's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,00:20:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I love this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,00:20:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Taromaru's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,00:20:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we have lots of fun, school will be lots of fun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,00:20:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,00:20:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,00:20:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your friend will come to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,00:20:26.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So don't look so sad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,00:20:29.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,00:20:32.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,00:20:35.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,00:20:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were talking about how much fun we had today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,00:20:40.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,00:20:45.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I hope tomorrow, and the day after, \Nand all the days to come are all this fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,00:20:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's swim in the pool tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,00:20:51.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You really are so immature, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,00:20:53.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh-whaa...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,00:20:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's go underground tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,00:20:59.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to try finding that evacuation area?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,00:21:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope there's good stuff down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,00:21:02.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,00:21:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,00:21:09.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel like just going to bed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,00:21:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, don't you want dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,00:21:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,00:21:14.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right, we still have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,00:21:19.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We're all pretty tired, so why don't we \Nmake something simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,00:21:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We had some Yamatoni canned beef left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,00:21:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I wanna have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,00:21:27.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, we have lots left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,00:21:29.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We've got some canned mackerel \Nand canned salmon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,00:21:31.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Canned grilled chicken could be good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,00:21:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so fancy, Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,00:22:40.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Talking on our way home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,00:22:45.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Telling each other our secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,00:22:51.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even when the 5-o'clock chime rings out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,00:22:56.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I feel we still haven't talked enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,00:23:03.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,A tiny four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,00:23:08.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sways in the gentle breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,00:23:13.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm sure that yes, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,00:23:20.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,I hope tomorrow will be sunny, too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,00:23:25.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,We walked the road together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,00:23:31.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Always saying we'd meet at the usual place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,00:23:35.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Ah, the fluffy clouds above
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,00:23:41.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Seem like they'll be burned, they're shining so bright
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,00:23:46.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even if, one day, these days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,00:23:52.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Are but a faded memory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,00:23:57.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,I want to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,00:24:04.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,A lot of smiles right now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,00:24:06.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,Next Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,00:24:09.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you're a witch, Ri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,00:24:10.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what they call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,00:24:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aw man, I want a nickname, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,00:24:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, then. How about the "Demon-Witch of Trouble"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,00:24:17.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,The Demon-Witch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,00:24:17.58,Caption2,,0,0,0,,of Trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,00:24:17.58,Caption3,,0,0,0,,(by Yuri)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,00:24:17.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Demon-Witch of Trouble"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,00:24:20.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,A Rainy Day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,00:24:20.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Next time on School-Live, episode 10: \N"A Rainy Day"
